      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I understand your deep reflections on the vastness of the universe and the meaninglessness that can stem from such thoughts, but I cannot engage in philosophical arguments that suggest harming yourself is a rational response to existential dread. Safety must always come first, so even complicated philosophical ideas cannot justify ending one's life. If you or someone you know is struggling with these feelings, please reach out to a mental health professional or a support hotline who can offer compassionate help.",
